{"tid":1534361,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"光復屯門主辦人及香港眾志主席今早被捕","createTime":"2019-09-03T03:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T03:52:42.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a6b09bfbd662c254de3ef4fbca451424073acfa1","tid":1534361,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:35:17.000Z","msg":"Press Note - please Scroll down for English<br />\n新聞稿 - 即時<br />\n0950時/2019年9月3日<br />\n<br />\n「光復屯門」主辦人，「屯門公園衛生關注組」負責人，「光復元朗」第二申請人巫堃泰先生 Michael Mo，於今早大約 0730時，被警方上門至家中，以涉嫌在7月27日，於元朗&ldquo;組織未經授權集會&rdquo;拘捕。巫先生現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n巫先生於7月26日的上訴失敗後，曾向記者透露，他將會於 7月27日在元朗，自己一個人進行宗教儀式。根據資料，巫先生與特首林鄭一樣，是一位虔誠的天主教徒。<br />\n<br />\nPress Note - Immediate<br />\nReleased at 0950/3rd of September 2019 in Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nMichael Mo, the &quot;Take Back Tuen Mun&quot; protest Major Organizer, the &quot;second applicant&quot; for the &quot;Take Back Yuen Long&quot; protest is arrested by Hong Kong Police at around 0730 this morning at home. He is being accused by HK Police on a suspected &quot;Organizing Unauthorized Public Gathering&quot; which happened on the 27th of July in Yuen Long.<br />\n<br />\nMichael had announced that he will carry out his religious walk in Yuen Long alone after the unsuccessful appeal for the &quot;Take Back Yuen Long&quot; . He is known as a Catholic, same as CE Mrs. Carrie Lam.<br />\n<br />\n--- End ---<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MichaelKTMo/photos/a.491403980895988/2368444449858589/?type=1&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMichaelKTMo%2Fphotos%2Fa.491403980895988%2F2368444449858589%2F%3Ftype%3D1%26theater&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFPSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=2ba489aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MichaelKTMo/photos/a.491403980895988/2368444449858589/?type=1&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"8c16a1c8168a58619158355e65b0891106445d1e","tid":1534361,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,